projects.mainTitle: Water and Sewer System Extension to Crawford State Park, Highway 92 Bore
mainContent: The Water and Sewer System Extension to the Crawford State Park was completed for the Town of Crawford to supply domestic water and sewer to the Crawford State Park.
The project included the construction of approximately 75-feet of steel casing pipe bored under Highway 92 south of the Town of Crawford.
